snippet.title: Midnight Murder Club - Early Access Trailer | PS5 & PC Games
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/midnight-murder-club/

Welcome to the Midnight Murder Club, where every decision counts. Armed with only a gun and a flashlight, you and your friends must navigate through a darkened mansion. Engage in a thrilling game of perception, deception, and sharpshooting.

Wildcards: Add unpredictable twists and rule-breaking effects to each match, keeping everyone on their toes and making every round unique. Chaos is in the cards! 

Guest Pass Edition: Invite up to five friends for free, increasing the fun and potential victims. All game modes and twists are available, ensuring no one misses out on the thrills.

#ps5 #ps5games #pcgames #midnightmurderclub
